{
  "stem": "25831.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they were there, my father said to the Gestapo men, I have to go upstairs to pack my bag.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "May I do that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very polite and said, yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father went upstairs, took that pill which he had prepared, and which he had shown me before, and died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my mother came back from downtown, the Gestapo people were still in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were very polite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are very sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We don't want to question you too much right now because of this condition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we will be back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother said, 'back for you.' But maybe they just said we will be back to ask you some questions.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my mother understood this to mean that she would be taken next.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so my grandfather, age 80, came immediately from Berlin and took my mother out of the house and took her to Berlin to where he lived.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think this is about the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do have a few more minutes?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When my mother came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to get my mother out of Germany was very difficult because I had to get a visa for the United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we did get it [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the last minute.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my mother needed some money for the steamship.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only an Italian line could've taken her because Germany was already at war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she came with a little suitcase via Trieste.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had paid for the ticket from here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was probably a third-class ticket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when my mother arrived she weighed maybe 85 pounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she looked terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when she saw me, she cried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, I killed your father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
